Action codes when plotting sprites
#Parent OS_SpriteOp
Value	Meaning
#Line
0	Overwrite
1	Disjoin (OR)
2	Conjoin (AND)
3	Exclusive Disjoin (EOR)
4	Invert screen
5	Identity (No change)
6	Conjoin Negation (AND with NOT sprite colour)
7	Disjoin Negation (OR with NOT sprite colour)
8-15	As 0-7, but with mask
16	Use palette instead of translation table when plotting 1/2/4/8bpp to 16/32bpp	(3.50+)
32	Translation table is 'wide'					(3.60+)
64	Dither when plotting a 16 or 32bpp sprite into a reduced depth	(3.60+)
128	Use colourmapping (16bpp / 32bpp only)				(Select 2)
